  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Creating markets for responsible timber from VPA countries</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Markets for responsible timber from VPA countries will be created through a roadshow of Responsible Timber Trade Fair events, timber promotional events, and continuous market promotion activities. Activities will be carried out in five VPA countries (Indonesia, Vietnam, Republic of Congo, Cameroon and Ghana) and two consumer markets (EU and China). Through these activities, VPA and FLEGT timber from the focal VPA counties will be promoted, as well as the promotion the European and Chinese legal trade of timber.  This will lead to an improved trade of legal timber from VPA countries.</narrative>
  </description>
